1. Glupane, zašto si to uradio? (Stupid, why did you do that?)
2. Ne razumem te, glupane jedan. (I don't understand you, you stupid person.)
3. Zar stvarno misliš da ću da uradim to, glupane? (Do you really think I'm going to do that, stupid?)
4. Nemoj da si glupane pa da poveruješ u to. (Don't be stupid and believe that.)
5. Kakav si ti to glupane da ne shvataš očigledne stvari? (What kind of stupid person are you that you don't understand obvious things?)
6. Glupane, budi malo pametniji i ne radi to. (Stupid, be a bit smarter and don't do that.)
7. Ne volim kad me neko naziva glupanom. (I don't like it when someone calls me stupid.)
8. Glupane jedan, zar ne vidiš da to nije dobra ideja? (You stupid person, can't you see that it's not a good idea?)
9. Nećeš valjda da radiš tako nešto, glupane? (You're not really going to do something like that, stupid?)
10. Nemoj da me zoveš glupanom, ja znam šta radim. (Don't call me stupid, I know what I'm doing.)